messages.content: ComfyUI_3dPoseEditor is a custom node that extends the capabilities of ComfyUI by providing a 3D pose editor.
What is the source of the 3D pose editor used in ComfyUI_3dPoseEditor?
The 3D pose editor used in ComfyUI_3dPoseEditor is sourced from open-pose-editor.
What was updated in ComfyUI_3dPoseEditor on 2024.01.04?
On 2024.01.04, the load method was rewritten, and issues #1, #2, and #4 were fixed with the help of @ltdrdata.
What is the name of the node set pose ControlNet in ComfyUI_3dPoseEditor?
The name of the node set pose ControlNet in ComfyUI_3dPoseEditor is _3D Pose Editor_.
Under which ComfyUI category does the _3D Pose Editor_ node fall?
The _3D Pose Editor_ node falls under the `image/3D Pose Editor` category in ComfyUI.
What should you do if your ComfyUI interface is not responding?
If your ComfyUI interface is not responding, you should try to reload your browser.
What is the issue with Efficient Nodes KSampler when using the same feed in ComfyUI_3dPoseEditor?
When using the same feed in the Efficient KSampler output, the output will not change if the pose editor is changed, possibly due to KSampler caching.
